    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, so i got prescribed some antibiotics for this skin infection on my arm. i've been taking them for 3 days now and the redness and swelling are basically gone. i feel totally fine. is it okay if i just stop taking them now since the infection seems to be gone? i dont really want to take more chemicals than i actually need",
